{"tid":308033,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［你問我答]就嚟放榜講下私院護士學校啦","createTime":"2017-07-03T22:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T19:10:25.000Z","uid":80649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0d410ef9bf39f8e135545dd90f42c7fd96ca8c2","tid":308033,"uid":80649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T22:06:09.000Z","msg":"見隔離有人開post講HA Nursing school我又開下post講私院nursing school啦 <br />\n隔離post好多人問嘅嘢呢到答左先啦<br />\n1.中學無讀理科讀唔讀得？<br />\n好多同學都無讀理科，不過會跟得辛苦啲<br />\n2.en有咩course<br />\nen多數都係私院開，有養x,仁x,法國...今年社署同ou一齊搞en course，但係ha今年就好似停左無開<br />\n3.en course大概會收幾多分<br />\n其實唔定，好睇interview，如果in得好我見過dse有2有3都有offer，in得差話之你考得幾好都byebye<br />\n4.interview形式係點？<br />\n主要係自我介紹先，再小組討論，通常一中一英，有機會俾新聞你睇完再討論，如果過到就會有second in問下你點解想做護士，屋企嘢，傾下計咁<br />\n利申返緊night好得閒，只要唔自爆嘅問題都盡量答，希望幫到下一幫dse雞or有興趣想做護士嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06fc5f5bf0c5e5fc4af344cfaae6a421ade75dde","tid":308033,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T22:54:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b75cc4cfc794a1a998ead52dacbefc9c97f32c5a","tid":308033,"uid":13992,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:00:21.000Z","msg":"私院邊間收男仔多，我知養和收勁少男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf270038a98b02c8f660d410f0e507ab7eb8852","tid":308033,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:01:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bab6d1340bdef6a949118e39e5c32b8262c58ce6","tid":308033,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:02:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b22ed18248d51ccc1d33f6f582ec8b58bbb3eef","tid":308033,"uid":80649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係睇樣？</blockquote><br />\n有啲私院係睇下你寄去張相順唔順眼先再睇你份申請表 樣ok學歷ok先叫你嚟interview睇下你個人係咪醒醒目目 你諗下一年幾千人報點睇得咁多"},{"pid":"c4f7cdaccccd3d94a94d72010738e0c84fb73b07","tid":308033,"uid":80649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私院邊間收男仔多，我知養和收勁少男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實私院間間都收少啲男仔 俾你係有錢佬入院都想有靚女護士serve你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a3ec392539ccbf587655cc0cd872d980eff55c","tid":308033,"uid":80649,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:49:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解呢行啲人成日詆譭HKU Nursing <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每間nursing school同u出嚟嘅人都有唔style 我就覺得普遍hku nursing出嚟嘅都好似覺得自己好叻唔洗跟人學嘢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都唔可以一碌鳩打一船人嘅 都有同事係hku nursing出嚟好做得嘢"},{"pid":"87cabe719c61218eb61ebadec8289f922aa38905","tid":308033,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T23:51:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45c479e56c106974d21ac0faca237e9160137283","tid":308033,"uid":80649,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T00:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>私院邊間收男仔多，我知養和收勁少男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實私院間間都收少啲男仔 俾你係有錢佬入院都想有靚女護士serve你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你係女？</blockquote><br />\n利申藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83a6142222166429ae439897b289531eb7f0c6e","tid":308033,"uid":29780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"想知養和收生標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講en course都收好高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ba85558baae902f2a543c2f87784bddc895083","tid":308033,"uid":80